Desiree Cousteau shines as the bubble headed Peaches of the title. This movie is pretty funny for an adult movie. Cousteau stands out in her role above all others in the movie. I first watched this movie in the 70's and became a big fan of Desiree Cousteau! She has haunted my dreams ever since in a good way and I loved her "innocent" demeanor that was very compelling. This DVD had greater production than I expected and I am most pleased to finally have this in my collection!

One of the classics of the 70's.  To make this movie then, you had to have actual camera equipment.  The plot is stupid, the acting at times terrible, and the idea that Peaches could be so gullible stretches the imagination.  But a lot is tongue in cheek, so stop being so critical and enjoy a raunchy movie for what is it.  A piece of early history when porn became available.  This movie was quite daring for its time.
